{"data":{"publications":{"edges":[{"node":{"id":"0013452e-cd11-55fa-93df-d1cdbeaf7bb6","html":"<p>Our undergraduate thesis examined mental health among physically challenged individuals versus the general population in Bangladesh during the COVID-19 pandemic. Using data from 22 physically challenged and 71 general participants, we found that interpersonal support positively correlates with well-being in both groups, while age negatively impacts well-being among general participants. A Random Forest–based machine learning model achieved over 93% accuracy in classifying the groups. The findings highlight distinct mental health factors and the need for tailored support strategies.</p>","frontmatter":{"title":"Understanding the Mental Health of Physically Challenged People and General People through Statistical and Machine Learning Approach","venue":"Asian CHI Symposium","external":"https://osf.io/preprints/psyarxiv/pjt46_v1","ResearchGate":null,"tech":null,"cover":{"childImageSharp":{"gatsbyImageData":{"layout":"fixed","placeholder":{"fallback":"data:image/png;base64,"},"images":{"fallback":{"src":"/static/31914ddca13eee34119f2fb2a60e7273/82c11/th-1.png","srcSet":"/static/31914ddca13eee34119f2fb2a60e7273/82c11/th-1.png 500w,\n/static/31914ddca13eee34119f2fb2a60e7273/13677/th-1.png 1000w","sizes":"500px"},"sources":[{"srcSet":"/static/31914ddca13eee34119f2fb2a60e7273/a61b1/th-1.avif 500w,\n/static/31914ddca13eee34119f2fb2a60e7273/9ef3c/th-1.avif 1000w","type":"image/avif","sizes":"500px"},{"srcSet":"/static/31914ddca13eee34119f2fb2a60e7273/5f169/th-1.webp 500w,\n/static/31914ddca13eee34119f2fb2a60e7273/3cd29/th-1.webp 1000w","type":"image/webp","sizes":"500px"}]},"width":500,"height":500}}}}}},{"node":{"id":"98a64b6c-2d78-59b1-a717-cd4d9a1f0cff","html":"<p>This study addresses the rising road accidents in Bangladesh, highlighting factors such as low traffic awareness and reckless driving. The proposed system uses eye-blink and ultrasonic sensors to control vehicle speed and prevent collisions—detecting driver drowsiness and monitoring obstacles in real time. While effective in improving highway safety, the system currently lacks location tracking and emergency alert features, which are identified for future enhancement.</p>","frontmatter":{"title":"Automatic Speed Control and Accident Avoidance Of vehicles using Multiple Sensors: In the Context Of Bangladesh","venue":null,"external":"https://www.researchgate.net/publication/353315532_Automatic_Speed_Control_and_Accident_Avoidance_Of_vehicles_using_Multiple_Sensors_In_the_Context_Of_Bangladesh","ResearchGate":null,"tech":null,"cover":{"childImageSharp":{"gatsbyImageData":{"layout":"fixed","placeholder":{"fallback":"data:image/png;base64,"},"images":{"fallback":{"src":"/static/c73ff3bf658e773348732813a2d114b4/8b27a/aut.png","srcSet":"/static/c73ff3bf658e773348732813a2d114b4/8b27a/aut.png 342w","sizes":"342px"},"sources":[{"srcSet":"/static/c73ff3bf658e773348732813a2d114b4/1c8eb/aut.avif 342w","type":"image/avif","sizes":"342px"},{"srcSet":"/static/c73ff3bf658e773348732813a2d114b4/7ab00/aut.webp 342w","type":"image/webp","sizes":"342px"}]},"width":500,"height":500}}}}}}]}}}